  "summaries": [
    "<b>Scorpion</b> and <b>Black Scorpion</b> are <linked>critters</linked>. As all other critters, they have 5 health, no defense, and are often killed instantly by other enemies or the player. They are most commonly found in a <linked>Desert</linked>. For detailed spawning conditions, see <linked>Notes</linked>.",
    "Scorpions can be caught using a <linked>Bug Net</linked>. They can be used as <linked>baits</linked> for <linked>fishing</linked>. They can be carried around in the <linked>inventory</linked> and released later, or crafted into a <linked>Scorpion</linked>/<linked>Black Scorpion Cage</linked>. Caged Scorpions cannot be released once crafted.",
    "The Scorpion Cage occupies a 6×3 space. The Scorpion inside may follow the following patterns randomly:",
    "<ul><li>Run from one side to the other of the cage</li><li>Submerge in sand</li><li>Stab with its stinger for a few times</li><li>Wave its stinger</li><li>Snip with its chelae</li></ul>"
